===Verb===
{{en-verb}}
# {{lb|en|intransitive}} Of a small [[dog]], to [[bark]].
# {{lb|en|intransitive|slang}} To [[talk]], especially [[excessively]]; to [[chatter]].
#: {{ux|en|You’re always '''yapping''', I wish you’d shut up.}}
# {{lb|en|transitive|slang}} To [[rob]] or [[steal]] from (someone).
#* {{quote-book|en|year=2000|passage=Ante up! '''Yap''' that fool!|author={{w|M.O.P.}}|title=Ante Up}}
